changelog.release_notes:
- Unlimited number of devices in App;
- New devices types:
   - Dimmers,
   - RGB switches;
- Scene activation;
- Device filtering (in settings);
- Updated icons.

- Fixed crash on start for networks with more than 8 devices;
- Do not show devices marked as permanently hidden;
- Other minor bugfixes.

data.description:
ZWay Time application allows you to control your RaZberry based smart home. 

It supports controls: 
- on-off switches;
- dimmers;
- RGB switches;
and sensors:
- motion;
- humidity; 
- light;
- temperature sensors. 

It can activate scenes as well. 

Devices are grouped into locations and can be filtered.

Do not hesitate to email me to add support of new device types.

